# Project (always read)

**STRD** — Blake Zajac portfolio/marketing site. Work in progress; follow existing patterns before introducing new architecture.

## Stack

- Astro 5 (`output: "server"`), `@astrojs/vercel`, MDX, sitemap, Sass, Zod content collections
- Site URL: `https://blakezajac.com` — sync `astro.config.mjs` `site` ↔ `src/lib/site.ts` `SITE_URL`
- Fonts: Typekit in `Layout.astro`; token `$font-family-01`

## Commands

`npm run dev` · `npm run build` · `npm run preview`

## Source layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/components/` | Astro UI (PascalCase `.astro`) |
| `src/layouts/` | `Layout.astro`, `ContentLayout.astro` |
| `src/pages/` | Routes + `api/` |
| `src/content/` | MDX collections + static JSON |
| `src/lib/` | Shared TS (schema, SEO helpers) |
| `src/actions/` | Astro Actions (contact → Resend) |
| `src/scss/style.scss` | **Only** global CSS entry (imported in `Layout.astro`) |
| `public/` | Static assets |

**Do not edit `dist/`** as source. No Gulp — Vite/Astro compile everything.

## Rule files (detail by area)

| File | When it applies |
|------|-----------------|
| `astro.mdc` | `src/**/*.astro` |
| `scss.mdc` | `src/scss/**` |
| `typescript.mdc` | `src/lib`, `actions`, `content/config`, `pages/api` |

## New UI checklist

1. Component in `src/components/` + BEM classes  
2. SCSS partial + register in `style.scss`  
3. `js-*` on nodes used by script; script in owning `.astro`  
4. Type/spacing from `_type-styles.scss` / `_variables.scss`  
5. MQ4: `(width >= …)` / `(width < …)`  
6. Content: extend `content/config.ts` + MDX/JSON — **no CMS**

## Tone & deploy

- Australian English; sentence case for headings/buttons unless design says otherwise  
- Contact: `/contact/?source=...` for campaign tracking  
- Vercel adapter; env: `RESEND_*` for form — never commit `.env`
